{"type": "article", "id": 23669, "title": "圆孔中看指针的手表", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-11T08:24:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702112452DUy38IKO2bNXvFWo.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是瑞典品牌 Tingest 推出的 2016 年新款手表，他们称灵感源于芭蕾舞裙的薄纱。表盘上覆盖了一面带孔的圆盘，指针在下面形成了填色块，看起来有点朦胧。设计师故意让圆点分布地较为随意，不会让圆孔本身变得紧张。手表使用日本石英机芯，表带是摩洛哥革，产品目前还没有上市。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112450PSqIFwDT7ZuosOki.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112450cXrWUZ8IA7NVvo0f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.34166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112451xnWV8HJB3UCOhKir.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.29666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112451ATeyzu0cmRV5xYBD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}